text: There are seven national parks in Austria, all of them internationally accepted according to the IUCN standard. Austria's national parks are: * Donau-Auen National Park * Gesäuse National Park * Hohe Tauern National Park * Kalkalpen National Park * Neusiedler See – Seewinkel National Park * Nockberge National Park * Thayatal National Park Austria Austria
title: National parks of Austria
